Well,  In Skyfire, there is a mob named an Acient Wyvern <lvl 60>.  4 Mages and one necro all between 55 and 51 took him out.  The necro was summoned after 10 seconds into the fight <over burn> and died. So that left 4 mages to kill him off.  The AW quads for 275 and has warrior hp.  He went through 7  lvl 51 earth pets.  After that he dropped like 5 gp is all.  <P>  The AW is not terribly hard at all. This is just an example of the mages power on a non casting mob.  The power is defined by this,  we all had over 75% mana left when done.  <IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/eq/biggrin.gif"><P><BR>Moark
