At 52 I grouped in KC with 4 other mages 50-53.  Nothing could beat the pets.  At first we just hung around at the cubby hole and killed everything and anything that moved.  We also cleared the small trains. =)  It was really really easy.  Perhaps the only thing that had to done was to debuff once in a while on the tough mobs.  When faced with several mobs we just let the earth pet tank for a bit while the rest of the pets killed the others one by one.  If need be, we sometimes broke up and duoed/soloed the multiple pulls we'd get.  After we got an enchanter (clarity II) and a monk, we took hand/warlord.  All in all, good fun and really easy. =P
